{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:"}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L753","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"}},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view that requested the annotation view."}]}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The object representing the annotation that is about to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The view object to display for the given annotation or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to display an annotation image instead."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method or have it return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" for that annotation, then implement"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" instead."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" is an instance of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" (or equal to the map view’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property), return an instance of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(or a subclass thereof)."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" to use for a given ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"text":" object on your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"map."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample","title":"Custom Annotation View","abstract":[{"text":"Add a custom annotation view","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","kind":"article"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapViewDelegate"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","title":"MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","title":"MLNUserLocation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property of the map view displayed in your application."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"View representing an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" on screen."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"}}}